</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="5">5</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/index.php?title=%D0%91%D0%BE%D0%B6%D1%8C%D1%8F_%D0%9C%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B5%D1%80%D1%8C_%D0%B2_%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%B2%D1%8B%D1%85_%D1%81%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%B3%D0%B0%D1%85_(%D0%90%D0%B9%D0%BF%D0%B8%D0%BD)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Редактировать раздел «5»">ред.</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
